# Sports

## Our Shows

### Big Monday Night in
The perfect end to the worst day of the week, a review of the weekends football! Join us Monday 6-7pm!

### Tuesday Sports Hour
Let Alex Duke cover as many sports as possible, joined by members of URN talking about every sport bar football. Also every week members of UoN Sports societies come on and say why they love their sport! Tuesday 6-7pm

### Saturday Social
Your companion as the Saturday sports begins! If you can’t keep up with all the weekends sports.... This is the show for you! Saturday 2-3pm!

### Whistleblowers
There is not a show like this… no seriously there is nothing to compare this to! The hungover sports chats we all love to have, a side ways look at the world of sport every Sunday 11am-12pm!
